WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.790
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.350 --> 02:49.990
[Episode 23]

02:51.840 --> 02:53.200
Is Yue okay?

02:56.010 --> 02:57.450
Actually, I shouldn't have

02:57.480 --> 02:58.950
told him about those things from the past.

02:59.200 --> 03:00.820
Yue's reserved and quiet.

03:01.010 --> 03:02.570
He didn't have many friends

03:02.600 --> 03:03.920
when he was in the Baize Clan.

03:04.400 --> 03:05.240
Now,

03:05.260 --> 03:07.010
I'm so glad to see him be friends

03:07.040 --> 03:08.200
with you, Ms. Bai.

03:09.240 --> 03:11.330
Hope you can help cheer him up.

03:11.640 --> 03:12.890
Actually,

03:12.910 --> 03:14.190
it's not all his fault.

03:14.780 --> 03:16.060
What happened to the Baize Clan

03:16.320 --> 03:19.090
is the greatest pain and regret in his heart.

03:19.110 --> 03:21.280
He has been missing you all these years.

03:21.690 --> 03:23.390
I'm also happy to see you two

03:23.420 --> 03:24.950
reunited now.

03:25.300 --> 03:26.150
Yue is now

03:26.180 --> 03:28.170
the esteemed Demon King of the Polar Region.

03:28.650 --> 03:30.040
He's shared the past

03:30.060 --> 03:30.970
and his weaknesses

03:31.000 --> 03:32.220
with you.

03:32.950 --> 03:35.200
I bet you matter a lot to him.

03:36.010 --> 03:37.440
He also means a lot to me.

03:40.890 --> 03:42.100
Have a good rest.

03:42.120 --> 03:42.960
I'll take my leave.

03:57.360 --> 03:58.180
You're awake.

04:01.170 --> 04:01.980
I

04:02.250 --> 04:03.240
was just passing by.

04:04.630 --> 04:05.490
Come in.

04:11.250 --> 04:12.600
If you have anything to say,

04:12.620 --> 04:13.630
just go ahead.

04:14.060 --> 04:15.570
You had a sudden headache yesterday.

04:15.840 --> 04:16.930
How is it now?

04:17.980 --> 04:19.100
Are you worried about me?

04:20.589 --> 04:21.640
As you said,

04:21.670 --> 04:23.950
we are in the same boat here at the Cold Spring Palace.

04:24.180 --> 04:25.740
Of course I should care about you.

04:26.920 --> 04:28.920
I fought my way out of those extraordinarily treacherous places.

04:28.950 --> 04:30.310
Injuries are nothing new to me.

04:30.330 --> 04:31.560
A little headache

04:31.580 --> 04:32.780
is nothing.

04:32.810 --> 04:34.440
But it's quite weird.

04:34.490 --> 04:35.950
I've had headaches for no reason.

04:36.210 --> 04:37.130
Pretty sure

04:37.460 --> 04:38.900
yesterday was the third time.

04:39.640 --> 04:41.070
Do you have any other symptoms

04:41.450 --> 04:43.150
besides the headache?

04:43.870 --> 04:44.830
Some images

04:44.830 --> 04:46.320
flashed through my mind,

04:46.380 --> 04:47.640
but I couldn't see clearly.

04:47.790 --> 04:49.740
There seemed to be some sounds as well,

04:50.159 --> 04:51.960
but I couldn't remember now.

04:53.940 --> 04:54.880
Did I

04:55.360 --> 04:56.790
say something

04:56.820 --> 04:58.310
that made you so concerned?

05:02.650 --> 05:03.730
You were

05:03.760 --> 05:05.670
actually mumbling something.

05:07.010 --> 05:08.130
but I didn't catch it.

05:09.730 --> 05:11.130
You're hiding something from me.

05:11.470 --> 05:12.740
What can I hide from you?

05:12.820 --> 05:14.630
Looks like your headaches

05:14.810 --> 05:16.610
are just from your overthinking.

05:17.100 --> 05:18.310
If I didn't think too much,

05:18.340 --> 05:19.860
I wouldn't have made it this far alive.

05:25.930 --> 05:27.100
Are you leaving already?

05:27.350 --> 05:28.420
I have something to attend to.

05:35.270 --> 05:36.150
The tranquilizer.

05:49.600 --> 05:50.960
You've been up all night?

06:07.210 --> 06:08.160
Tastes good.

06:11.860 --> 06:13.810
I hope you're really letting it go

06:13.950 --> 06:15.660
instead of pretending.

06:24.950 --> 06:25.950
Knowing the truth

06:25.970 --> 06:27.750
is to face it better,

06:27.780 --> 06:30.300
but not to be stuck in past guilt.

06:31.120 --> 06:32.420
Don't forget that

06:32.490 --> 06:34.460
we came to the Stone Clan's place not only to investigate the case

06:34.490 --> 06:35.620
but also to gather the Contemplations.

06:35.690 --> 06:36.920
Only by gathering the Five Contemplations

06:36.920 --> 06:38.840
and undoing the Seven Stars Soul Burning Seal on you as soon as possible

06:38.860 --> 06:40.860
can you protect the people around you better.

06:51.960 --> 06:52.960
I'm so lucky to have you

06:54.370 --> 06:55.140
by my side.

06:58.840 --> 07:00.200
The Stone Clan's place

07:00.580 --> 07:01.870
is full of danger now.

07:02.800 --> 07:04.020
After dark,

07:04.130 --> 07:05.270
let's go to the stone forest

07:05.270 --> 07:06.120
for investigation.

07:06.520 --> 07:08.560
I also want to know why these victims

07:08.590 --> 07:10.660
were all killed in the stone forest at night.

07:16.250 --> 07:17.160
Seems that you got here

07:17.160 --> 07:18.160
one step ahead of me, Ms. Bai.

07:18.530 --> 07:19.600
I'll head out and leave you

07:19.820 --> 07:20.820
to your meal.

07:20.850 --> 07:21.720
Why not join us?

07:29.010 --> 07:30.070
I remember

07:30.070 --> 07:31.660
you used to love these bamboo-stuffed buns.

07:31.680 --> 07:32.600
I asked Mrs. Cang.

07:32.630 --> 07:33.430
She told me

07:33.430 --> 07:35.159
the bamboo shoots here only grow in the back mountain.

07:35.180 --> 07:37.140
So I went there early this morning to dig these fresh bamboo shoots.

07:37.190 --> 07:37.990
Give it a try.

07:38.480 --> 07:39.890
You don't have to over-exert yourself for me.

07:43.700 --> 07:44.690
Qi Feng,

07:44.930 --> 07:46.580
you just came here, so you may not know

07:46.850 --> 07:48.090
it's not safe

07:48.120 --> 07:49.280
in the Stone Clan right now.

07:49.640 --> 07:51.690
You'd better not go out alone.

07:52.220 --> 07:53.940
Now that you and Fan Yue are finally reunited,

07:53.960 --> 07:56.460
your safety is very important to him.

07:56.590 --> 07:58.050
My bad for being reckless.

07:58.330 --> 07:59.390
I just wanted to let Yue

07:59.390 --> 08:00.750
try my cooking.

08:02.470 --> 08:04.170
I'm not blaming you.

08:04.200 --> 08:05.610
You're right, Ms. Bai.

08:05.630 --> 08:06.920
Now I'm disabled

08:06.950 --> 08:07.940
with weak spiritual power.

08:07.960 --> 08:09.300
I'd be pretty helpless

08:09.330 --> 08:10.910
if I really ran into danger.

08:11.330 --> 08:12.260
Qi Feng,

08:12.650 --> 08:13.940
Shuo is caring about you.

08:15.180 --> 08:16.010
Don't worry.

08:16.940 --> 08:17.920
I'm here,

08:18.230 --> 08:19.670
and I will protect you.

08:24.120 --> 08:26.120
Since it used to be Fan Yue's favorite,

08:26.160 --> 08:27.230
let me try it too.

08:27.260 --> 08:28.500
Thank you, Qi Feng.

08:33.080 --> 08:34.559
Ms. Bai, with your amazing cooking,

08:34.580 --> 08:35.370
Yue can enjoy

08:35.400 --> 08:36.429
a lot of delicacies from now on.

09:12.400 --> 09:13.170
Mrs. Cang,

09:13.190 --> 09:14.150
let me help you.

09:14.170 --> 09:16.210
Don't bother, Ms. Bai. I can do it myself.

09:16.670 --> 09:18.030
It's okay, Mrs. Cang.

09:18.050 --> 09:19.080
We're lodging in your house.

09:19.100 --> 09:20.680
Helping out is the least we can do.

09:20.710 --> 09:22.110
Thank you.

09:24.650 --> 09:26.200
I heard from Shi Lei that

09:26.230 --> 09:27.630
the Stone Clan has no grudges outside

09:27.670 --> 09:28.650
with peace inside.

09:28.680 --> 09:30.160
You guys have no enemies.

09:30.180 --> 09:31.540
But with no enemies,

09:31.560 --> 09:34.470
your clan members were actually tortured to death.

09:35.180 --> 09:36.910
You went all the way to the Unbridled Pavilion

09:36.930 --> 09:38.810
and anxiously asked Master Fan for help.

09:38.830 --> 09:40.560
But we've been here for two days.

09:40.580 --> 09:42.700
Yet you didn't urge us to find your husband.

09:42.730 --> 09:44.170
Aren't you worried?

09:45.120 --> 09:46.310
Or

09:46.620 --> 09:47.900
are you waiting for something?

09:50.570 --> 09:52.850
What's the use of worrying?

09:52.880 --> 09:53.880
Master Fan

09:53.900 --> 09:55.630
has his own way of investigation.

09:55.650 --> 09:56.980
I'm just

09:57.010 --> 09:58.280
an ignorant woman.

09:58.300 --> 10:00.350
So I can only wait for him to solve the case.

10:00.730 --> 10:02.930
But you don't look like you know nothing.

10:04.150 --> 10:05.070
Mrs. Cang,

10:05.100 --> 10:06.910
the murder case of the Stone Clan is still unsolved.

10:07.250 --> 10:09.820
I hope you don't hide any information.

10:11.390 --> 10:12.290
I...

10:12.580 --> 10:13.660
Mrs. Cang,

10:14.920 --> 10:17.090
I heard that the wind chimes under the eaves are broken.

10:17.110 --> 10:18.660
I made you a new one.

10:18.690 --> 10:20.140
Hope you like it.

10:22.180 --> 10:23.050
What?

10:23.320 --> 10:24.480
You don't like it, Mrs. Cang?

10:33.280 --> 10:35.190
I've got soup simmering in the kitchen.

10:35.220 --> 10:35.950
I'll go take a look.

10:36.000 --> 10:37.000
I'll leave the space for you.

10:37.410 --> 10:38.340
Mrs. Cang,

10:43.740 --> 10:44.990
the kitchen is that way.

10:46.100 --> 10:47.660
Well, I'm getting old.

10:47.690 --> 10:49.810
I can't even tell the direction.

10:54.170 --> 10:55.950
Why are you looking at me like that, Ms. Bai?

10:55.980 --> 10:56.860
Nothing.

10:56.880 --> 10:58.950
I just think your craftsmanship

10:58.980 --> 11:00.490
is way better than I thought.

11:00.510 --> 11:02.730
Although God took away my legs,

11:02.860 --> 11:05.050
I've still got a pair of hands to make a living.

11:05.270 --> 11:06.620
That's kind of him.

11:06.650 --> 11:07.970
If you need anything,

11:07.990 --> 11:09.120
just tell me.

11:09.150 --> 11:10.280
At least,

11:10.300 --> 11:11.860
I can help with something this way.

11:52.180 --> 11:54.080
The Heavenly Sky Fan?

11:54.110 --> 11:55.960
You are the Master of Cold Spring Palace?

12:24.020 --> 12:25.660
He's even set a barrier.

12:25.690 --> 12:26.950
Looks like this mirror

12:26.980 --> 12:28.780
means a lot to Zhen Yu.

12:34.230 --> 12:36.270
You shouldn't be here.

12:39.350 --> 12:40.140
Master,

12:40.890 --> 12:41.960
I came to report the recent movements

12:41.960 --> 12:43.010
of the Eternals and demons

12:43.030 --> 12:44.120
and didn't find you in the room.

12:44.120 --> 12:44.900
I planned to...

12:45.480 --> 12:47.090
Is this what you meant when you said

12:47.110 --> 12:48.780
you'd be the strongest among the Ladies and Lords

12:48.810 --> 12:50.340
by my side?

12:50.760 --> 12:52.000
So strong that

12:52.030 --> 12:54.640
you could even enter my room

12:54.670 --> 12:56.650
and pry into my secret at will.

12:57.200 --> 12:58.550
Do you know that,

12:58.580 --> 13:00.300
with a little squeeze,

13:00.320 --> 13:02.040
I could just

13:02.060 --> 13:04.110
crush your head?

13:04.130 --> 13:05.290
I didn't intend

13:05.320 --> 13:07.080
to pry into your secret, Master.

13:07.100 --> 13:08.980
I just accidentally hit it.

13:30.270 --> 13:31.390
Master!

13:33.970 --> 13:34.970
Master...

13:36.570 --> 13:38.300
Chong Zhao broke into your room

13:38.330 --> 13:39.170
for...

13:39.680 --> 13:40.930
It was for me.

13:42.290 --> 13:43.630
For you?

13:45.230 --> 13:47.830
Chong Zhao knew I was punished and was worried,

13:47.850 --> 13:49.970
so he broke into your room to look for the elixir.

13:50.000 --> 13:51.740
He definitely didn't mean to offend you, Master.

13:51.770 --> 13:53.400
Please forgive him

13:53.420 --> 13:54.400
and spare his life.

13:54.420 --> 13:55.690
Really?

13:57.040 --> 13:57.870
Yes.

14:03.250 --> 14:04.450
Don't think that

14:04.530 --> 14:06.470
you're indispensable to the Cold Spring Palace.

14:06.610 --> 14:07.780
In this world,

14:07.810 --> 14:08.690
no one

14:08.710 --> 14:10.020
is irreplaceable.

14:10.100 --> 14:11.150
I understand.

14:12.690 --> 14:14.120
I understand.

14:14.770 --> 14:15.560
Get lost!

14:33.710 --> 14:34.590
I told you

14:34.730 --> 14:36.100
everything in the Cold Spring Palace

14:36.130 --> 14:37.600
is under the Grand Master's control.

14:37.630 --> 14:39.320
How dare you break into his room without permission?

14:39.340 --> 14:40.380
And as I said,

14:40.410 --> 14:41.920
we're even now.

14:41.950 --> 14:43.190
You don't have to speak up for me anymore.

14:43.210 --> 14:44.730
Do you really want to die?

14:44.760 --> 14:46.270
Sometimes, it may seem like a path to death,

14:46.300 --> 14:48.650
yet it might actually give more people a chance to survive.

14:48.670 --> 14:49.550
Back in the Outlanders' City, Zhen Yu

14:49.550 --> 14:51.120
already ignored the order of Eternals and demons.

14:51.140 --> 14:53.020
What is the plot he's working on now?

14:53.050 --> 14:54.770
This concerns world peace.

14:55.750 --> 14:57.080
I have to dig into it

14:57.590 --> 14:59.060
even at the risk of my life.

14:59.800 --> 15:00.810
So,

15:01.270 --> 15:02.490
what did you find?

15:02.580 --> 15:04.220
An ancient mirror with cracks.

15:04.250 --> 15:05.730
Have you heard of it from him before?

15:05.750 --> 15:06.630
An ancient mirror?

15:07.990 --> 15:10.150
I've never heard the Grand Master mention it before.

15:11.190 --> 15:12.030
But why did he

15:12.030 --> 15:13.790
let you go so easily today?

15:13.890 --> 15:15.130
You already went against his order

15:15.150 --> 15:17.190
and saved me from the secret chamber.

15:17.210 --> 15:18.990
Today, you even pried into his secret,

15:19.020 --> 15:21.090
yet he just accepted the excuse I made up and let you go.

15:22.360 --> 15:24.400
I think he found something

15:24.420 --> 15:25.620
on me.

15:35.130 --> 15:36.440
Did the Grand Master also spot

15:36.440 --> 15:38.150
the black forehead mark on Chong Zhao?

15:38.330 --> 15:39.940
I think I also sensed

15:39.970 --> 15:40.950
another sort of power from him,

15:40.980 --> 15:42.250
something other than demonic power.

15:42.520 --> 15:44.280
Something other than demonic power?

15:44.520 --> 15:45.810
You've never noticed it before?

15:48.340 --> 15:50.080
Am I the only one who can sense it?

15:50.760 --> 15:52.850
Why on earth did Zhen Yu let me go?

15:52.870 --> 15:53.900
Chong Zhao,

15:53.930 --> 15:55.450
You were lucky to be spared

15:55.470 --> 15:56.610
by the Grand Master.

15:56.820 --> 15:57.660
I'm afraid

15:57.680 --> 15:58.670
you can't dig up any secrets

15:58.690 --> 16:00.060
in the Cold Spring anymore.

16:00.240 --> 16:01.200
I suggest you

16:01.550 --> 16:02.570
go back to Lanling.

16:18.300 --> 16:20.040
Your soup smells so good, Mrs. Cang.

16:22.860 --> 16:24.720
Why are you so nervous?

16:24.970 --> 16:26.050
You've been acting well

16:26.080 --> 16:27.480
these past few days, haven't you?

16:28.260 --> 16:30.210
As you requested,

16:30.240 --> 16:32.000
I've lured the Master of Bright Moon here.

16:32.100 --> 16:34.340
When will you release my husband?

16:34.520 --> 16:36.540
It depends on whether you listen to me or not.

16:46.280 --> 16:47.680
After so many years,

16:48.560 --> 16:50.660
you're still so into bones, Mrs. Cang.

17:12.780 --> 17:14.510
Judging from the scratches

17:14.510 --> 17:16.349
and the holes all over these stones,

17:16.599 --> 17:18.240
it's clear that the murderer wielded some sharp

17:18.240 --> 17:19.680
steel weapons

17:19.910 --> 17:22.530
that could kill people with one blow,

17:22.680 --> 17:23.640
yet the murderer chose

17:23.640 --> 17:25.329
to break their bones and veins.

17:25.760 --> 17:27.240
Aside from torturing them,

17:27.260 --> 17:28.369
what else was the murderer up to?

17:31.810 --> 17:33.070
Maybe the victims

17:33.070 --> 17:34.270
share something in common.

17:34.630 --> 17:36.190
Something in common?

17:36.210 --> 17:37.060
No.

17:37.780 --> 17:39.260
They are all from different families.

17:42.370 --> 17:43.530
I got it.

17:43.860 --> 17:45.580
Before I left the Stone Clan,

17:45.610 --> 17:46.960
a host of clan members fell ill.

17:46.980 --> 17:48.630
I remember they were the ones who went out to find the elixir

17:48.660 --> 17:49.730
and cured everyone.

17:49.750 --> 17:51.030
Why didn't you tell us earlier?

17:51.610 --> 17:52.680
What disease did they get?

17:52.700 --> 17:53.980
And what elixir did they find?

17:54.010 --> 17:55.010
I don't know.

17:55.030 --> 17:55.710
I have to ask my mother.

17:58.730 --> 17:59.320
Who's there?

17:59.800 --> 18:00.480
Get him!

18:09.060 --> 18:10.180
Where are we?

18:10.810 --> 18:12.180
Why's the resentment aura so strong here?

18:12.920 --> 18:13.680
Master,

18:13.700 --> 18:14.420
Bai Shuo,

18:14.450 --> 18:15.490
let's go.

18:15.510 --> 18:17.820
This is the Forbidden Stone Formation of the Stone Clan.

18:37.360 --> 18:38.070
Are you okay?

18:38.180 --> 18:38.710
Master,

18:38.740 --> 18:39.450
I'm fine.

18:39.710 --> 18:41.450
I cut the man in black on the shoulder.

18:41.960 --> 18:43.330
That's so weird.

18:43.660 --> 18:44.590
That man in black seemed to have

18:44.590 --> 18:45.720
deliberately lured us here,

18:45.890 --> 18:47.160
held the two of us back,

18:47.190 --> 18:48.760
and only attacked Cang Shan.

18:49.090 --> 18:50.370
What on earth is his purpose?

18:50.800 --> 18:52.070
Let's go back first.

18:56.630 --> 18:58.480
What on earth is that stone formation for?

19:02.490 --> 19:04.290
Actually, we Stone Clan

19:04.320 --> 19:05.340
didn't live here before.

19:05.800 --> 19:06.800
Ten years ago,

19:06.820 --> 19:08.160
the Demon Race was awash with slaughter.

19:08.190 --> 19:10.150
Many clans were destroyed by the Tiger Clan.

19:10.240 --> 19:11.590
We Stone Clan were no exception.

19:12.280 --> 19:13.880
To avoid the hunting of the Tiger Clan,

19:13.900 --> 19:15.950
my father led the clan members to migrate everywhere.

19:15.980 --> 19:18.080
First, we reached a valley in the south.

19:18.100 --> 19:19.400
It abounded with spiritual energy,

19:19.420 --> 19:20.880
hidden in the mountains

19:20.900 --> 19:22.550
as a perfect place to live in seclusion.

19:23.530 --> 19:25.190
Our people wanted to settle there,

19:25.360 --> 19:26.730
but we found

19:27.280 --> 19:29.790
it was the home of another ancient clan.

19:30.330 --> 19:31.680
What ancient clan?

19:31.700 --> 19:32.730
I don't know.

19:32.920 --> 19:34.380
When we arrived,

19:34.400 --> 19:35.600
they were already wiped out.

19:36.020 --> 19:37.110
Only one young man was left,

19:37.110 --> 19:38.480
guarding the tombs of his family there.

19:39.320 --> 19:40.970
Our people had been wandering for too long.

19:41.300 --> 19:42.820
They didn't want to leave there.

19:44.410 --> 19:46.390
They wanted to occupy that valley by force.

19:47.140 --> 19:49.140
But that was the young man's home too.

19:49.880 --> 19:51.280
How would he let that happen?

19:51.810 --> 19:53.330
At the resting place of his family,

19:53.870 --> 19:55.300
if he had any guts left in him,

19:55.320 --> 19:56.390
he wouldn't give in.

19:56.700 --> 19:57.810
What did you do?

19:58.730 --> 20:00.430
That young man would rather die than leave his homeland.

20:01.490 --> 20:02.490
My father

20:03.300 --> 20:04.260
killed him.

20:05.140 --> 20:06.190
What?

20:06.970 --> 20:08.010
After he died,

20:08.040 --> 20:09.350
the resentment aura started to permeate

20:09.880 --> 20:11.620
and make trouble for the people of the Stone Clan.

20:12.490 --> 20:14.370
Our clan couldn't continue living there,

20:14.570 --> 20:16.170
so we had to migrate again

20:16.370 --> 20:17.410
to this place.

20:18.180 --> 20:19.570
But that young man's resentment aura

20:19.590 --> 20:20.470
followed us all the way,

20:20.490 --> 20:21.370
sticking around.

20:21.780 --> 20:22.700
My father

20:22.720 --> 20:23.510
and the other clansmen

20:23.530 --> 20:25.290
erected the stone pillars in the stone forest

20:26.080 --> 20:27.490
to suppress the resentment aura.

20:28.290 --> 20:30.650
That's the Stone Formation we've just been to.

20:31.120 --> 20:32.320
Seized someone's residence,

20:32.810 --> 20:34.120
killed the innocent,

20:34.610 --> 20:35.810
and suppressed his soul.

20:37.130 --> 20:39.080
No wonder that Stone Formation is a forbidden area.

20:40.190 --> 20:41.680
Did you refuse to return home

20:41.930 --> 20:43.670
because of this past incident?

20:43.910 --> 20:45.630
I had a big fight with my father.

20:45.820 --> 20:46.950
After that,

20:47.140 --> 20:48.420
I left the Stone Clan

20:48.450 --> 20:49.840
and never came back.

20:50.000 --> 20:51.650
The resentment aura in that Stone Formation

20:51.680 --> 20:53.270
is definitely not from the young man alone.

20:53.780 --> 20:55.570
Are you hiding anything else from me?

20:56.070 --> 20:57.400
I swear I've come clean.

20:57.680 --> 20:58.490
Master,

20:58.960 --> 20:59.720
please trust me.

21:00.190 --> 21:01.600
But if the last one

21:01.630 --> 21:03.810
of that ancient clan's bloodline was killed,

21:03.980 --> 21:05.820
who else would come to take revenge?

21:06.850 --> 21:08.410
Did you see

21:08.430 --> 21:09.910
that young man get killed?

21:10.660 --> 21:11.500
My father

21:12.190 --> 21:13.410
broke his legs.

21:13.440 --> 21:15.380
He bled all over the place with a hemorrhage.

21:15.400 --> 21:16.880
He couldn't survive.

21:18.200 --> 21:20.190
Your father broke his legs?

21:20.660 --> 21:22.830
Qi Feng's legs have suffered from an old injury as well.

21:23.170 --> 21:24.660
The timing of his appearance was too coincidental.

21:24.940 --> 21:25.550
What if...

21:25.550 --> 21:27.040
The world is full of coincidences.

21:27.090 --> 21:28.960
There are plenty of people with leg problems.

21:28.990 --> 21:30.400
This alone

21:30.420 --> 21:31.610
can't prove anything.

21:31.960 --> 21:33.220
I've checked it in person.

21:33.240 --> 21:35.800
Qi Feng's legs are indeed totally broken.

21:36.330 --> 21:37.760
The man in black

21:37.790 --> 21:39.490
we just saw in the Stone Formation

21:39.520 --> 21:40.970
has fully functional legs.

21:41.070 --> 21:42.290
He can't be Qi Feng.

21:45.360 --> 21:46.880
Fan Yue, don't think too much.

21:47.740 --> 21:49.690
Coincidences may not necessarily be the truth.

21:50.220 --> 21:51.940
Don't stress yourself out.

21:59.770 --> 22:00.610
Cang Shan,

22:01.140 --> 22:03.020
how old was that young man

22:03.150 --> 22:04.160
when his legs got broken?

22:04.600 --> 22:06.150
About 14 or 15 years old.

22:07.100 --> 22:08.530
In other words,

22:08.880 --> 22:10.380
he is about the same age as Fan Yue.

22:11.030 --> 22:11.790
Bai Shuo,

22:12.060 --> 22:13.800
didn't you just talk like you didn't suspect Qi Feng?

22:14.600 --> 22:15.840
It's not that I don't.

22:15.930 --> 22:17.820
I just don't want to suspect him in front of Fan Yue.

22:18.340 --> 22:19.400
He lost his entire family

22:19.400 --> 22:20.750
overnight that year.

22:21.000 --> 22:22.640
Now that he's finally got Qi Feng back,

22:22.890 --> 22:25.060
it's torture for him

22:25.090 --> 22:26.910
to suspect Qi Feng of the murder.

22:27.290 --> 22:29.400
Currently, it's pure speculation with no evidence.

22:29.500 --> 22:31.270
Before we find out the truth,

22:31.300 --> 22:32.980
there's no need to make Fan Yue sad.

22:35.620 --> 22:36.270
I see.

22:53.460 --> 22:54.060
Like this?

22:55.630 --> 22:57.660
The divination of three special children

22:57.710 --> 22:59.070
is about the ultimate secret of the world.

22:59.070 --> 23:00.830
We'd better not do it.

23:01.630 --> 23:02.520
You shall either divine

23:02.680 --> 23:03.720
or die.

23:05.370 --> 23:06.170
I'll do it...

23:06.200 --> 23:08.160
Let me do it...

23:34.590 --> 23:35.950
What does this mean?

23:35.980 --> 23:37.260
Baize Clan,

23:37.530 --> 23:39.000
purple-eyed boy.

23:41.660 --> 23:42.540
What's wrong with you?

23:42.700 --> 23:44.420
Oh, no...

23:44.450 --> 23:46.620
This divination is against God's will.

23:46.640 --> 23:48.820
I will get backlash!

23:49.200 --> 23:50.660
Then die!

23:50.730 --> 23:52.360
No, I'll do it...

23:52.400 --> 23:53.510
Let me continue.

24:14.270 --> 24:15.320
And what does this mean?

24:20.790 --> 24:21.310
You...

24:21.340 --> 24:23.630
What exactly are you making me divine?

24:23.650 --> 24:25.020
Don't ask about what you shouldn't know.

24:25.050 --> 24:25.850
Say it.

24:27.610 --> 24:28.570
Human Race,

24:28.590 --> 24:30.080
Ning'an City,

24:30.110 --> 24:31.310
Bai family.

24:32.350 --> 24:33.910
Bai family?

24:33.930 --> 24:34.790
Go on.

24:34.930 --> 24:37.210
I really can't divine the third one!

24:37.240 --> 24:38.170
Then die.

24:40.720 --> 24:43.830
It takes abundant spiritual energy for a Mystery Turtle

24:43.860 --> 24:47.010
to divine the top secret of the world.

24:47.030 --> 24:49.270
The first two children's information

24:49.300 --> 24:50.910
has used up my spiritual energy.

24:50.960 --> 24:52.400
Even if you kill me today,

24:52.400 --> 24:53.440
it's still beyond my capacity.

24:53.440 --> 24:54.590
Then I'll just kill you.

24:54.590 --> 24:55.440
Five years...

24:55.440 --> 24:56.310
Give me five years!

24:56.310 --> 24:58.200
Once I fuel myself with spiritual energy in five years,

24:58.200 --> 24:59.510
I'll surely help you divine

24:59.510 --> 25:00.930
where the third child is.

25:05.410 --> 25:06.220
Fine.

25:06.250 --> 25:07.250
Today I'll

25:07.270 --> 25:08.540
trust you this time.

25:09.550 --> 25:11.290
You have five years.

25:11.480 --> 25:12.530
Five years later,

25:12.560 --> 25:14.360
I'll come to you again.

25:19.010 --> 25:20.600
Don't try to play tricks.

25:20.620 --> 25:21.620
Otherwise,

25:21.680 --> 25:23.660
I'll make sure to eliminate all the Mystery Turtles

25:23.740 --> 25:25.520
in the Eastern Continent.

25:28.300 --> 25:30.220
According to the Mystery Turtle's divination,

25:30.240 --> 25:32.040
I've brought back the first two children

25:32.070 --> 25:33.680
from the Demon Race and Human Race.

25:35.160 --> 25:36.810
Do I really have to wait

25:37.220 --> 25:39.410
for two decades for the third child?

25:53.310 --> 25:55.570
The third child will be born...

25:55.970 --> 25:56.870
Where?

26:00.010 --> 26:01.390
The Eternal Race.

26:02.100 --> 26:02.970
When?

26:06.520 --> 26:07.720
Twenty years later.

26:08.220 --> 26:09.330
Twenty years later?

26:09.650 --> 26:10.410
Okay.

26:10.430 --> 26:11.500
In these 20 years,

26:11.530 --> 26:13.760
you should stay at the Cold Spring Palace with me.

26:14.030 --> 26:15.030
By then,

26:15.050 --> 26:16.490
you shall wait

26:16.760 --> 26:19.510
for the birth of that child with me.

26:31.610 --> 26:34.600
The third child shouldn't be born yet.

26:35.110 --> 26:36.500
But just now,

26:36.530 --> 26:37.820
I clearly saw that black forehead mark

26:37.840 --> 26:39.750
on Chong Zhao.

26:41.090 --> 26:43.170
Did that Mystery Turtle lie to me?

26:55.740 --> 26:56.650
My lord,

26:57.370 --> 26:59.050
I've been waiting for you for 60,000 years.

26:59.820 --> 27:01.190
It's been 60,000 years.

27:01.250 --> 27:03.210
Everyone thinks that all gods have perished,

27:03.240 --> 27:04.610
and the Hidden Race has fallen.

27:05.150 --> 27:06.580
No one knows that

27:06.720 --> 27:08.960
I've been holding onto the last bit of your hidden power

27:09.180 --> 27:10.710
all the time, my lord.

27:12.220 --> 27:14.290
I didn't have awareness 60,000 years ago.

27:14.310 --> 27:16.350
Although I can't remember your appearance,

27:16.380 --> 27:18.670
I've never forgotten your help.

27:18.880 --> 27:21.030
I won't mistake that black forehead mark.

27:21.700 --> 27:22.660
My lord,

27:23.440 --> 27:24.480
is it really you?

27:26.030 --> 27:26.990
My lord,

27:28.090 --> 27:29.250
I will find the Contemplation Stone

27:29.280 --> 27:30.810
and the three children

27:31.160 --> 27:32.000
with the Divine Race destiny

27:32.000 --> 27:33.350
as soon as possible

27:33.820 --> 27:34.890
to bring you

27:34.920 --> 27:36.110
back to the world.

27:37.350 --> 27:38.600
Soon,

27:38.930 --> 27:39.880
I won't need this Heavenly Mirror

27:39.880 --> 27:41.480
to reminisce you anymore.

27:43.240 --> 27:44.110
My lord,

27:45.090 --> 27:46.020
wait for me.

28:01.670 --> 28:02.360
Yue!

28:04.030 --> 28:06.200
Have you finished the investigation with Ms. Bai?

28:07.260 --> 28:08.850
With a murder in the Stone Clan,

28:09.290 --> 28:11.240
no one will feel at ease.

28:11.880 --> 28:14.190
After what happened to the Baize Clan back then,

28:14.230 --> 28:16.400
I felt like I died inside as well.

28:17.900 --> 28:19.420
You and I know the pain

28:20.160 --> 28:21.530
of losing family.

28:22.120 --> 28:23.670
If there's anything I can help,

28:23.840 --> 28:24.950
just feel free to reach out to me.

28:27.370 --> 28:28.050
Qi Feng,

28:29.490 --> 28:31.280
where were you when we entered the stone forest

28:32.120 --> 28:32.960
last night?

28:33.930 --> 28:35.200
I was in my room.

28:40.600 --> 28:41.650
Yue,

28:42.300 --> 28:43.500
are you suspecting me?

28:44.810 --> 28:46.810
There's something I want to ask you.

28:47.940 --> 28:49.560
Last time you didn't give me a straight answer

28:49.590 --> 28:50.910
about how your legs got broken.

28:52.060 --> 28:53.460
Can you tell me now?

28:53.840 --> 28:55.080
Who hurt you?

28:55.100 --> 28:56.690
Do you want to know who hurt me,

28:57.440 --> 28:58.980
or who I hurt?

29:01.740 --> 29:02.610
Yue,

29:03.590 --> 29:04.670
you don't trust me.

29:09.660 --> 29:10.870
We are brothers.

29:11.150 --> 29:12.910
Brothers never lie to each other.

29:13.180 --> 29:14.870
That's why I chose to ask you directly.

29:27.080 --> 29:29.800
Do you know what keeps you from passing away

29:30.230 --> 29:31.950
when the pain almost knocks you out?

29:36.320 --> 29:37.690
It's hope.

29:38.500 --> 29:40.300
I hoped I could survive.

29:40.860 --> 29:42.580
I hoped I could see you again.

29:43.670 --> 29:45.080
The Baize Clan was gone.

29:46.220 --> 29:47.850
You were the last one I've got.

29:49.010 --> 29:51.250
If I couldn't make it and died out there,

29:51.270 --> 29:53.100
how would you manage to live alone?

29:57.610 --> 29:58.940
This hope

30:00.480 --> 30:01.800
helped me pull through.

30:03.060 --> 30:04.370
But I didn't expect

30:05.570 --> 30:07.260
you to suspect me now.

30:11.280 --> 30:12.280
Qi Feng,

30:13.210 --> 30:13.890
I...

30:17.370 --> 30:18.530
What happened?

30:20.260 --> 30:21.030
What's wrong?

30:21.030 --> 30:21.720
I don't know!

30:22.770 --> 30:23.910
Come and take a look.

30:24.680 --> 30:25.990
He fell from the sky.

30:26.290 --> 30:27.440
This man

30:27.470 --> 30:29.280
just fell from the sky.

30:29.310 --> 30:30.800
If I hadn't dodged in time,

30:30.880 --> 30:32.510
he almost hit me.

30:40.940 --> 30:42.460
It's the one who attacked us last night.

30:43.100 --> 30:44.290
The attacker?

30:44.400 --> 30:45.240
What's going on?

30:45.240 --> 30:46.000
Who is it?

30:46.000 --> 30:47.000
What happened?

30:51.080 --> 30:51.790
Chief?

30:51.790 --> 30:53.070
Didn't the Chief go missing?

30:53.070 --> 30:54.000
What's going on?

30:54.000 --> 30:54.720
It's the Chief!

30:54.720 --> 30:55.750
Why is the Chief here?

30:56.890 --> 30:57.830
Chief?

30:57.850 --> 30:59.190
Is that true?

31:05.410 --> 31:07.030
How could it be the Chief?

31:06.820 --> 31:07.860
[Uncle Shi, Stone Clan, Demon Race]

31:07.030 --> 31:08.400
Chief?

31:19.350 --> 31:20.760
How could it be?

31:22.370 --> 31:24.140
Why did this happen all of a sudden?

31:27.430 --> 31:28.710
The Mountain-splitting Blade...

31:29.960 --> 31:31.330
The Mountain-splitting Blade?

31:32.850 --> 31:34.180
It was you...

31:34.980 --> 31:36.500
It was you!

31:37.200 --> 31:38.330
The wounds on the Chief

31:38.360 --> 31:40.080
were caused by the Mountain-splitting Blade!

31:40.100 --> 31:40.910
The Mountain-splitting Blade?

31:42.180 --> 31:43.140
Cang Shan,

31:43.170 --> 31:44.910
you killed the Chief!

31:45.310 --> 31:46.150
Father!

31:47.000 --> 31:48.280
Don't talk nonsense!

31:48.300 --> 31:49.700
Although the Mountain-splitting Blade is Cang Shan's weapon,

31:49.730 --> 31:51.360
how could he hurt the Chief?

31:52.480 --> 31:53.330
Cang Shan,

31:53.350 --> 31:54.650
explain it to us.

31:54.670 --> 31:56.080
C'mon! Defend yourself!

31:56.110 --> 31:57.650
What's there to explain?

31:59.850 --> 32:01.250
You bastard!

32:07.540 --> 32:09.500
Before we get to the bottom of it,

32:09.520 --> 32:10.890
no one can make a move.

32:12.090 --> 32:13.050
Father...

32:15.270 --> 32:16.380
It was me...

32:16.570 --> 32:17.700
I killed my father.

32:18.230 --> 32:19.530
I killed my father...

32:19.700 --> 32:20.650
I killed my father...

32:21.280 --> 32:22.550
I killed my father...

32:22.580 --> 32:23.620
I killed my father.

32:23.640 --> 32:24.680
I killed my father!

32:24.710 --> 32:25.950
Cang Shan!

32:30.240 --> 32:31.760
You have no conscience!

32:31.780 --> 32:32.610
Leave it to me.

32:34.660 --> 32:36.580
That bastard killed his father!

32:36.610 --> 32:37.860
Bastard!

32:37.880 --> 32:39.120
You bastard!

32:39.150 --> 32:40.390
Bastard!

32:44.060 --> 32:45.870
You are such a jerk!

32:49.370 --> 32:51.410
Bastard! Kill him!

32:51.440 --> 32:53.290
You watched Cang Shan grow up.

32:53.310 --> 32:55.410
You should know him well.

32:55.550 --> 32:57.020
Even though he was mad at his father,

32:57.050 --> 32:58.530
he would never kill his father!

32:58.550 --> 32:59.850
He wouldn't do it

32:59.880 --> 33:01.040
if he were sober.

33:01.060 --> 33:02.890
But when he relapses,

33:03.200 --> 33:04.910
he can't control himself at all.

33:04.940 --> 33:05.940
Everyone here knows that.

33:05.960 --> 33:07.650
Yes, we all know that.

33:12.310 --> 33:13.510
What do you mean

33:13.540 --> 33:14.530
by "relapse"?

33:14.680 --> 33:15.790
We Stone Clan members are born

33:15.810 --> 33:17.090
with stronger power than other demons.

33:17.650 --> 33:18.890
We don't know why

33:19.230 --> 33:21.230
Cang Shan was born with way more overwhelming power.

33:21.260 --> 33:22.020
I killed my father...

33:22.040 --> 33:23.880
He couldn't control this power before,

33:24.440 --> 33:25.290
often losing control

33:25.310 --> 33:26.220
and hurting our people.

33:26.340 --> 33:27.380
I killed my father...

33:27.410 --> 33:29.170
Since I met Cang Shan,

33:29.460 --> 33:31.400
I've never seen him lose control of his demonic power

33:32.020 --> 33:33.780
or hurt any random people.

33:33.810 --> 33:34.980
You haven't seen it,

33:35.090 --> 33:36.550
but it doesn't mean he won't.

33:37.130 --> 33:38.620
The Stone Clan has seen frequent murder cases.

33:38.640 --> 33:41.010
The Chief's mysterious death is fishy.

33:41.420 --> 33:43.370
Before we find out the truth,

33:43.390 --> 33:45.100
I won't let anyone do anything to Cang Shan.

33:46.810 --> 33:49.120
Master Fan, you are obviously biased.

33:49.140 --> 33:50.380
So what if I am?

33:51.230 --> 33:53.500
At least my bias is aboveboard.

33:53.850 --> 33:54.730
Unlike you,

33:55.060 --> 33:57.340
who have done plenty of selfish things

33:57.370 --> 33:58.740
yet still faking

33:58.770 --> 34:01.070
peace and love on the surface.

34:03.730 --> 34:05.080
What do you mean, Master Fan?

34:05.100 --> 34:06.610
You know

34:06.630 --> 34:08.370
exactly what I mean.

34:10.940 --> 34:11.980
I must

34:12.330 --> 34:13.830
bring Cang Shan back.

34:14.110 --> 34:15.909
You can try to stop me

34:17.610 --> 34:18.989
if you want.

34:20.300 --> 34:21.300
How arrogant!

34:21.330 --> 34:22.020
You...

34:22.300 --> 34:23.110
Father.

34:45.940 --> 34:51.050
♫What kind of flower would never bear fruit?♫

34:54.230 --> 34:59.870
♫What kind of fruit never sees a flower?♫

35:02.350 --> 35:10.420
♫Withstanding the stillness, you are a broken piece of me♫

35:10.700 --> 35:16.170
♫I am the fruit to your flowers♫

35:17.920 --> 35:19.390
How much longer

35:19.630 --> 35:21.540
are you going to mess around just for an outsider?

35:24.740 --> 35:26.410
You killed that young man,

35:26.440 --> 35:28.030
and now you're even trying to suppress his soul!

35:28.260 --> 35:29.820
Why do you care about

35:29.850 --> 35:31.040
an outsider?

35:31.310 --> 35:32.420
Everything I've done

35:32.450 --> 35:33.860
is for the Stone Clan!

35:33.880 --> 35:34.820
Cang Shan,

35:35.040 --> 35:36.290
I'm your father after all!

35:35.780 --> 35:39.690
♫Across thousands of miles♫

35:36.320 --> 35:37.390
No.

35:38.180 --> 35:39.060
My father

35:39.120 --> 35:41.290
is a great and righteous hero.

35:41.360 --> 35:44.170
He protects his clan with a kind heart.

35:44.110 --> 35:48.960
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

35:44.190 --> 35:46.300
He would never occupy someone's home

35:46.330 --> 35:48.430
and kill an innocent young man!

35:48.810 --> 35:49.520
You

35:49.540 --> 35:50.980
don't deserve to be my father!

35:51.730 --> 35:59.110
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

35:54.950 --> 35:55.890
Fine.

35:56.580 --> 35:58.620
I don't deserve to be your father, huh?

35:58.650 --> 36:00.470
Get out of the Stone Clan then!

36:00.120 --> 36:04.880
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

36:00.660 --> 36:02.180
Never come back.

36:02.210 --> 36:03.430
I'll treat it like you're dead,

36:03.450 --> 36:05.650
or I've never had a son like you!

36:10.400 --> 36:11.650
Get lost!

36:11.830 --> 36:17.810
♫What kind of tree never takes root?♫

36:19.870 --> 36:25.860
♫What kind of roots never turn into trees?♫

36:28.370 --> 36:35.680
♫To break the roots of love, to look at the past and seal one's heart♫

36:36.280 --> 36:41.270
♫I'm your wanderer♫

36:43.860 --> 36:48.170
♫The flowers flew away♫

36:46.110 --> 36:47.700
Why didn't I recognize you?

36:50.820 --> 36:51.860
Father...

36:52.030 --> 36:56.280
♫My tears are streaming down like rain♫

37:00.370 --> 37:07.330
♫Light my heart's lamp, cast away attachments, and ask the world♫

37:08.480 --> 37:14.010
♫On the vast sea, you and I♫

37:12.040 --> 37:14.240
He has locked himself in his room for quite a while.

37:14.580 --> 37:16.230
I'm worried that if this continues,

37:16.250 --> 37:17.410
he'll get stuck in overthinking

37:17.440 --> 37:18.290
and hurt himself.

37:18.960 --> 37:21.410
Mr. Cang Sr. has been missing for days, and he suddenly showed up last night.

37:21.440 --> 37:22.400
It was already suspicious.

37:22.890 --> 37:24.040
What's even weirder is that

37:24.220 --> 37:26.080
there's no way he couldn't recognize Cang Shan.

37:26.180 --> 37:27.970
So why would he attack Cang Shan?

37:28.310 --> 37:30.060
This is definitely not as simple as it seems.

37:30.500 --> 37:31.920
It was too chaotic

37:31.920 --> 37:33.300
to check it out just now.

37:33.360 --> 37:35.030
I plan to go to the stone house

37:35.050 --> 37:36.380
to check Mr. Cang Sr.'s body.

37:37.180 --> 37:38.060
Let's go together.

37:55.760 --> 37:57.710
Didn't you promise me

37:57.860 --> 38:00.300
you would let him go

38:00.690 --> 38:02.050
if I did what you said?

38:03.220 --> 38:04.690
Why did you kill him?

38:05.090 --> 38:06.530
Why?

38:06.980 --> 38:09.550
You were going to tell Bai Shuo the truth yesterday,

38:09.580 --> 38:10.370
weren't you?

38:12.010 --> 38:13.100
One

38:13.130 --> 38:14.920
must pay for betrayal.

38:15.880 --> 38:18.320
But I didn't say it.

38:19.180 --> 38:22.370
Yet you went back on our deal.

38:23.230 --> 38:25.230
Then let me fulfill my promise now

38:27.350 --> 38:29.500
and send you to reunite with your husband.

38:53.700 --> 38:54.860
Your bones and veins are complete.

38:55.180 --> 38:56.810
Apart from the wounds on his body,

38:57.110 --> 38:58.840
there seem to be no other fatal injuries.

39:00.660 --> 39:02.370
But when he got injured last night,

39:02.400 --> 39:04.750
he could still fight off Cang Shan and escape.

39:04.940 --> 39:06.350
Why did he suddenly die?

39:15.820 --> 39:16.840
What is this?

39:27.750 --> 39:28.630
There's something inside.

39:41.780 --> 39:43.380
Guess it was this evil insect

39:43.930 --> 39:45.690
that controlled Mr. Cang Sr.'s mind

39:45.890 --> 39:47.240
and got him killed without him even realizing it.

39:48.070 --> 39:49.800
Controlled his mind?

39:50.120 --> 39:52.000
This sounds like...

39:52.400 --> 39:53.450
The Cold Spring Palace's trick.

39:57.680 --> 39:59.220
Mr. Cang Sr. was the Chief of the Stone Clan

39:59.940 --> 40:01.830
with quite superior spiritual power among the demons.

40:02.960 --> 40:05.460
Yet this evil insect could actually control his mind.

40:06.180 --> 40:07.290
I'm curious

40:07.610 --> 40:09.480
how this evil insect was raised.

40:10.280 --> 40:11.490
Do you know how these evil insects

40:11.520 --> 40:12.690
control humans?

40:13.220 --> 40:14.580
There are many kinds of poisonous insects in the world.

40:14.790 --> 40:16.420
I've never seen this sort of evil insect before.

40:17.340 --> 40:18.670
But since it's a poisonous insect,

40:18.690 --> 40:20.070
there must be another one paired with it.

40:20.450 --> 40:22.240
With the parent insect, the mastermind can just

40:22.370 --> 40:24.260
control countless sub insects at the same time.

40:26.500 --> 40:28.500
If we find the parent insect and destroy it,

40:28.520 --> 40:30.560
will that disable all the sub insects?

40:31.510 --> 40:32.550
That makes sense.

40:33.090 --> 40:34.080
But the mastermind

40:34.100 --> 40:35.780
won't hand over the parent insect so easily.

40:36.040 --> 40:38.020
Besides, the parent insect has absorbed all the poisonous energy.

40:38.120 --> 40:39.870
It can't be busted so easily.

40:40.880 --> 40:42.810
Our collection of the Contemplation in the Stone Clan is really risky this time.

40:44.400 --> 40:45.540
As I said before,

40:45.590 --> 40:46.350
so long as I'm here...

40:46.380 --> 40:48.090
Who said only you can protect me?

40:48.450 --> 40:49.740
I can protect you as well.

40:53.490 --> 40:55.920
Cang Shan's still locking himself in his room.

40:56.130 --> 40:57.130
He might need you,

40:57.160 --> 40:58.490
his master,

40:59.020 --> 41:01.230
to help him work through the trauma caused by his father's death.

41:01.250 --> 41:02.210
Besides Cang Shan,

41:02.930 --> 41:03.700
there's another person

41:04.710 --> 41:05.840
who should spill the secrets

41:05.840 --> 41:07.190
hidden by the Stone Clan all these years.

41:07.750 --> 41:08.920
You mean

41:09.200 --> 41:09.880
Mrs. Cang?

41:09.880 --> 41:10.600
Exactly.

41:10.620 --> 41:13.020
The mastermind controlled Mr. Cang Sr. with evil insects.

41:13.490 --> 41:14.170
Who's there?

41:14.300 --> 41:16.040
He lured us to the forbidden area of the Stone Clan first,

41:16.720 --> 41:18.590
deliberately letting Cang Shan hurt his father.

41:18.830 --> 41:20.280
Then Cang Shan was framed for killing his father.

41:21.610 --> 41:23.600
Every step was carefully orchestrated.

41:23.620 --> 41:25.560
There's no way the Stone Clan doesn't have enemies.

41:26.000 --> 41:27.380
I even think

41:27.400 --> 41:29.640
the murderer's been targeting Cang Shan.

41:29.810 --> 41:31.250
We're totally on the same page.

41:31.720 --> 41:32.920
So we must

41:32.920 --> 41:34.140
get to know the past grudges

41:34.170 --> 41:36.290
of the Stone Clan before the next accident.

41:50.010 --> 41:51.870
You lock yourself in the room

41:52.180 --> 41:54.190
without sleeping, resting, drinking, or eating.

41:54.480 --> 41:55.920
Your mother will be worried.

41:56.960 --> 41:59.160
"You don't deserve to be my father."

42:01.460 --> 42:03.930
This is the last thing I said to him.

42:04.620 --> 42:07.270
He asked me to get out of the Stone Clan and never come back.

42:08.370 --> 42:10.780
I've really been away for so many years

42:11.540 --> 42:13.120
without coming back even once.

42:14.460 --> 42:15.480
I thought I would never forgive him

42:15.510 --> 42:16.600
for the rest of my life.

42:17.250 --> 42:19.410
But when he died in front of me,

42:19.760 --> 42:21.950
I realized that I didn't want to lose him at all.

42:32.230 --> 42:34.220
I know you feel so guilty and down,

42:34.360 --> 42:36.520
blaming yourself for not returning to the Stone Clan earlier,

42:37.250 --> 42:39.220
not recognizing your father,

42:39.490 --> 42:40.970
and striking that blow.

42:42.480 --> 42:44.230
But I want to tell you that, Cang Shan,

42:44.870 --> 42:46.730
it's not your fault.

42:47.230 --> 42:48.630
Before your father attacked you,

42:48.630 --> 42:51.020
an evil insect already controlled his mind.

42:51.050 --> 42:52.820
He already couldn't recognize you.

42:53.400 --> 42:54.580
Bai Shuo and I

42:54.700 --> 42:56.270
found an evil insect

42:56.440 --> 42:58.010
in your father's body.

42:58.300 --> 42:59.900
It was the insect that controlled him.

43:00.700 --> 43:02.940
And your father didn't die from a stab wound.

43:03.260 --> 43:05.660
He was killed by the evil insect that devoured his demonic essence.

43:06.830 --> 43:07.730
Master,

43:07.760 --> 43:08.920
who on earth murdered

43:08.920 --> 43:10.340
my father and my clansmen?

43:10.410 --> 43:12.090
Just because we don't know who did that,

43:12.290 --> 43:14.720
you must pull yourself together, and let's find out the truth

43:15.250 --> 43:16.610
to let the dead rest in peace.

43:18.250 --> 43:19.850
But that can't bring them back to life.

43:20.530 --> 43:21.520
I understand.

43:22.140 --> 43:23.340
With the family gone,

43:24.280 --> 43:25.450
all that's left is regret.

43:26.350 --> 43:29.060
Even the strongest Eternals and demons in the world will have their regrets.

43:29.950 --> 43:31.680
Regret is just a part of life.

43:32.610 --> 43:33.740
Since it's inevitable,

43:34.370 --> 43:35.850
we can't let us get stuck in it.

43:36.630 --> 43:37.990
We should learn to move on.

43:38.380 --> 43:39.740
Let's try together.

43:46.510 --> 43:47.800
Ms. Bai, where are you going

43:47.800 --> 43:48.710
in such a hurry?

43:49.630 --> 43:50.980
I need to talk to Mrs. Cang.

43:51.030 --> 43:51.890
Mrs. Cang?

43:52.250 --> 43:53.910
I think she went to the back mountain to pick vegetables.

43:54.010 --> 43:56.050
I saw her walking out with a basket.

43:56.840 --> 43:58.350
Mr. Cang Sr. just died,

43:58.370 --> 44:00.410
yet Mrs. Cang's already doing chores

44:00.480 --> 44:01.840
like nothing happened?

44:12.900 --> 44:13.950
I know

44:14.060 --> 44:15.170
I'm an outsider.

44:15.690 --> 44:17.470
There were multiple murders within the Stone Clan

44:17.690 --> 44:19.400
while I showed up at this time.

44:19.430 --> 44:21.720
It's reasonable for you to suspect me more or less.

44:22.650 --> 44:23.430
Ms. Bai,

44:23.690 --> 44:24.830
I can take my leave now.

44:25.250 --> 44:26.400
May fate bring Yue and me

44:26.630 --> 44:28.360
back together again in the future.

44:29.170 --> 44:30.520
The world is big.

44:30.540 --> 44:32.230
I believe there will be a place for me to settle.

44:33.010 --> 44:34.790
Please tell Yue about this.

44:35.760 --> 44:37.110
I won't say goodbye to him face-to-face.

44:37.660 --> 44:39.370
You and Fan Yue just reunited in your real identities.

44:39.890 --> 44:41.430
Do you really want to leave?

44:44.090 --> 44:46.000
Do you want me to stop you?

44:46.020 --> 44:48.150
Or do you want Fan Yue to blame me for not keeping you?

44:49.060 --> 44:50.440
Ms. Bai, you got me wrong.

44:51.150 --> 44:52.500
I'm just afraid

44:52.520 --> 44:54.370
I can't bear to bid farewell to Yue.

44:54.960 --> 44:55.960
And I'm also worried

44:55.990 --> 44:57.260
I might delay your investigation.

44:59.740 --> 45:00.780
Watch out!

45:05.740 --> 45:07.650
Qi Feng? Qi Feng!
